                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<h2>Tour of Britain Women 2025: How to watch</h2>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"646\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-970x646.jpg\" alt=\"peloton of women cycling past classically british houses\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/05/GettyImages-womens-tour-peloton-2022-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Justin Setterfield/Getty Images</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Information on how to watch the Tour of Britain Women will be revealed soon.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Live TV and streaming times</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><em>All times BST and subject to change by broadcasters</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Stage 1: Dalby Forest – Redcar, Thursday 5th June</h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Coverage:</strong> TBC</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Stage 2: Hartlepool – Saltburn-by-the-Sea, Friday 6th June</h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Covarage:</strong> TBC</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Stage 3: Kelso – Kelso, Saturday 7th June</h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Coverage:</strong> TBC</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Stage 4: Glasgow – Glasgow, Sunday 8th June</h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Coverage:</strong> TBC</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tour of Britain Women 2025: Start list</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Team line-ups are not yet fully confirmed, so the list is subject to change pre-race</em></p>\n\n\n\n<div><p><em>Data powered by <a href=\"https://firstcycling.com/race.php?r=9063&amp;y=2025&amp;k=8\" target=\"_blank\">FirstCycling.com</a></em></p></div>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/tour-of-britain-women-preview\">Tour of Britain Women 2025: Route, how to watch and everything you need to know</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Ewan Wilson &#124; Staff Writer","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"9585ccb6e83b616db2a753c5e96813da5347f4147c4e8ca58a364dd031b1b847","category":"Cycling"}